      "title": "Coverage gaps (honest)",
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 5,
        "w": 24,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**Covered:** API `route=search` P95 (`markhand:api_search:p95_5m`) vs G0-SLO-QUERY-P95 (0.5s); search availability ratio vs SLA 99.5%.\n\n**Coverage gap / blocked:** filtered-query P99 (G0-SLO-QUERY-P99) is **not emitted** by O01 \u2014 alert lives in `alert_rules.blocked.yml` and is not loaded. Internal retrieval-leg latency is **not** used as end-to-end SLO."
      }
    },
